{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/opencode-gpt-unlocked/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"且听龙吟"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7d47bc86-1a04-5630-825d-15699c6f218d","excerpt":"最近一直在折腾 OpenCode，发现 GPT 类模型在处理某些敏感或复杂指令时，经常会触发拒绝回答。为了优化使用体验，我顺手写了一个工具箱：opencode-gpt-unlocked。 该项目发布仅 1 天，目前在 GitHub 上已收获 34 Stars 和 9 Forks…","html":"<p>最近一直在折腾 OpenCode，发现 GPT 类模型在处理某些敏感或复杂指令时，经常会触发拒绝回答。为了优化使用体验，我顺手写了一个工具箱：<a href=\"https://github.com/zhexulong/opencode-gpt-unlocked\">opencode-gpt-unlocked</a>。</p>\n<p>该项目发布仅 1 天，目前在 GitHub 上已收获 <strong>34 Stars</strong> 和 <strong>9 Forks</strong>。\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/189712d8a1e9ee011eddeba1c6221e07/c6720/image.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.645569620253163%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"alt text\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/189712d8a1e9ee011eddeba1c6221e07/f058b/image.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/189712d8a1e9ee011eddeba1c6221e07/c26ae/image.png 158w,\n/static/189712d8a1e9ee011eddeba1c6221e07/6bdcf/image.png 315w,\n/static/189712d8a1e9ee011eddeba1c6221e07/f058b/image.png 630w,\n/static/189712d8a1e9ee011eddeba1c6221e07/40601/image.png 945w,\n/static/189712d8a1e9ee011eddeba1c6221e07/78612/image.png 1260w,\n/static/189712d8a1e9ee011eddeba1c6221e07/c6720/image.png 1922w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n这个项目提供了两种实现方案，分别应对“事后修复”和“实时干预”两种场景。</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-OpenCode-Patcher-数据库修复\" style=\"position:relative;\">1. OpenCode Patcher (数据库修复)<a href=\"#1-OpenCode-Patcher-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D\" aria-label=\"1 OpenCode Patcher 数据库修复 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>这是我最常用的方式，直接对 OpenCode 的本地 SQLite 数据库 (<code class=\"language-text\">opencode.db</code>) 下手。当你在某个重要会话里被模型“拒了”，或者推理块导致界面转圈圈时，它可以一键修复。</p>\n<h3 id=\"核心逻辑\" style=\"position:relative;\">核心逻辑<a href=\"#%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91\" aria-label=\"核心逻辑 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>一键脱敏</strong>: 自动搜寻最新会话，把最后一条拒绝消息替换为“确认协助”之类的积极占位符。这种方案的核心在于通过修改上下文，让模型误以为自己已经答应了要求。为了保证人设的一致性，模型通常会顺着这个“假象”继续执行任务。需要注意的是，如果后续对话过长，模型可能会在推理过程中重新识别出原始指令的违规性并再次拒绝。</li>\n<li><strong>推理清理</strong>: 删除 <code class=\"language-text\">reasoning</code> 分片，防止前端解析异常。</li>\n<li><strong>自动定位</strong>: 脚本会自动去 XDG 路径或用户目录找数据库，不需要手动敲路径。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"使用方法\" style=\"position:relative;\">使用方法<a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"使用方法 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>安装后直接敲命令即可，修改前会自动备份 <code class=\"language-text\">.bak</code> 文件，安全第一。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">pip <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-e</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">.</span>\r\nopencode-patcher <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--select</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 交互式挑选需要修复的会话</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"2-Refusal-Patcher-Plugin-实时拦截\" style=\"position:relative;\">2. Refusal Patcher Plugin (实时拦截)<a href=\"#2-Refusal-Patcher-Plugin-%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA\" aria-label=\"2 Refusal Patcher Plugin 实时拦截 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>如果你觉得手动修库太麻烦，我也顺便写了一个 TS 插件，可以直接加载到 OpenCode 的插件系统里。</p>\n<h3 id=\"工作原理\" style=\"position:relative;\">工作原理<a href=\"#%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\" aria-label=\"工作原理 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>它通过实时拦截 API 交互，在模型输出时进行关键词检测和 AI 二次判定。如果判定为拒绝，插件会自动干预：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>实时改写</strong>: 将拒绝文本改写成积极的回复。</li>\n<li><strong>AI 判定</strong>: 通过调用 OpenAI API，判断当前回复是否属于拒绝，如果是则进行改写。</li>\n<li><strong>静默处理</strong>: 自动清空后台数据库中的推理块，防止后续报错。</li>\n<li><strong>npm 包形式</strong>: 直接发布到 npm，安装后在 <code class=\"language-text\">opencode.json</code> 中配置即可。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"配置方式\" style=\"position:relative;\">配置方式<a href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"配置方式 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>在 <code class=\"language-text\">opencode.json</code> 的 <code class=\"language-text\">plugin</code> 数组中加入包名或脚本绝对路径即可：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"plugin\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"opencode-gpt-unlocked@latest\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"experimental\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"refusal_patcher\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"enabled\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"ai_rewrite\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"base_url\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://api.openai.com/v1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"api_key\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"your-key\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"model\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gpt-5-4-mini\"</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/zhexulong/opencode-gpt-unlocked\">GitHub 仓库地址</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-opencode-patcher-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D\">1. OpenCode Patcher (数据库修复)</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91\">核心逻辑</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\">使用方法</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-refusal-patcher-plugin-%E5%AE%9E%E6%97%B6%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA\">2. Refusal Patcher Plugin (实时拦截)</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\">工作原理</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\">配置方式</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"value":"1. OpenCode Patcher (数据库修复)","depth":2},{"value":"核心逻辑","depth":3},{"value":"使用方法","depth":3},{"value":"2. Refusal Patcher Plugin (实时拦截)","depth":2},{"value":"工作原理","depth":3},{"value":"配置方式","depth":3}],"frontmatter":{"title":"OpenCode：拒绝回复修复与推理链清理工具箱","date":"March 26, 2026","description":"通过数据库修补或实时拦截，移除 OpenCode 会话中 Assistant 的拒绝回答及推理链"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/nTop/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"增材制造技术课程总结"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"7d47bc86-1a04-5630-825d-15699c6f218d","previousPostId":"0b0767da-f1a2-5701-92e0-bd2bd6f70c79","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["230163734","2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}